  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will enroll completers of a prior 24 week MEMS cap study of Kaletra adherence,
      conducted in 2005 - 2006, and repeat the MEMS monitoring for an additional 24 weeks in
      2008/2009 on the current antiretroviral anchor drug. The goals of the study are to correlate
      long-term adherence with virologic outcome, and to explore the stability of MEMS cap
      adherence measurements over time.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
